#: l10n/source/edge.xml:142
msgid ""
"Where <literal>$SCC_REGISTRATION_CODE</literal> is the registration code "
"copied from <link xl:href=\"https://scc.suse.com/\">SUSE Customer Center</"
"link>, and the package list contains <literal>jq</literal> w hich is "
