#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:414
msgid ""
"Each build creates a time-stamped folder in <literal>$CONFIG_DIR/_build/</"
"literal> that includes the logs of the build, the artifacts used during the "
"build, and the <literal>combustion</literal> and <literal>artefacts</"
"literal> directories which contain all the scripts and artifacts that are "
"added to the CRB image."
msgstr ""
"Para cada imagen se crea una carpeta con marca de tiempo en "
"<literal>$CONFIG_DIR/_build/</literal> que incluye los registros del proceso "
"de creación, los artefactos utilizados durante la creación y los directorios "
"<literal>combustion</literal> y <literal>artefacts</literal>, que contienen "
"todos los guiones y artefactos que se añaden a la imagen lista para arrancar."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:415
msgid "The contents of this directory should look like:"
msgstr "El contenido de este directorio tendrá este aspecto:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:416
msgid ""
"If the build fails, <literal>eib-build.log</literal> is the first log that "
"contains information. From there, it will direct you to the component that "
"failed for debugging."
msgstr ""
"Si la compilación falla, <literal>eib-build.log</literal> es el primer "
"registro que contiene información. Desde allí, se le dirigirá al componente "
"que falló para su depuración."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
