#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:549
msgid "GitOps"
msgstr "GitOps"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:550
msgid ""
"Rancher includes Fleet as a built-in component to allow manage cluster "
"configurations and application deployments with code stored in git."
msgstr ""
"Rancher incluye Fleet como un componente integrado para permitir la gestión "
"de configuraciones de clústeres y despliegues de aplicaciones con código "
"almacenado en git."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:551
msgid "Observability"
msgstr "Observabilidad"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:552
msgid ""
"Rancher includes built-in monitoring and logging tools like Prometheus and "
"Grafana for comprehensive insights into your cluster health and performance."
msgstr ""
"Rancher incluye herramientas integradas de supervisión y registro, como "
"Prometheus y Grafana, que proporcionan información detallada sobre el estado "
"y el rendimiento del clúster."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:553 l10n/source/edge.xml:923 l10n/source/edge.xml:945
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1065
