#: l10n/source/edge.xml:565
msgid ""
"All of the SUSE Edge 3.4 components, including dashboard extensions, are "
"distributed as OCI artifacts. To install SUSE Edge Extensions you can use "
"Rancher Dashboard UI, Helm or Fleet:"
msgstr ""
"Todos los componentes de SUSE Edge 3.4, incluidas las extensiones de panel "
"de control, se despliegan como artefactos OCI. Para instalar extensiones de "
"SUSE Edge, puede usar la interfaz del usuario del panel de control de "
"Rancher, Helm o Fleet:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:566
msgid "Installing with Rancher Dashboard UI"
msgstr "Instalación con la interfaz de usuario del panel de control de Rancher"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:567
msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis> in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis> section of the navigation sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis> (Extensiones) "
"en la sección <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis> "
"(Configuración) de la barra lateral de navegación."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:568
msgid ""
"On the Extensions page, click the three dot menu at the top right and select "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Manage Repositories</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"En la página Extensions (Extensiones), haga clic en el menú de tres puntos "
"de la parte superior derecha y seleccione <emphasis role=\"strong\">Manage "
"Repositories</emphasis> (Gestionar repositorios)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:569
msgid ""
"Each extension is distributed via its own OCI artifact. They are available "
"from the SUSE Edge Helm charts repository."
msgstr ""
"Cada extensión se despliega mediante su propio artefacto OCI. Están "
"disponibles en el repositorio de charts de Helm de SUSE Edge."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:570
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Repositories page</emphasis>, click "
"<literal>Create</literal>."
msgstr ""
"En la página <emphasis role=\"strong\">Repositories</emphasis> "
"(Repositorios), haga clic en <literal>Create</literal> (Crear)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:571
msgid ""
"In the form, specify the repository name and URL, and click <literal>Create</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"En el formulario, especifique el nombre y la URL del repositorio y haga clic "
"en <literal>Create</literal> (Crear)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:572
msgid ""
"SUSE Edge Helm charts repository URL: <literal>oci://registry.suse.com/edge/"
"charts</literal>"
msgstr ""
"URL del repositorio de charts de Helm de SUSE Edge: <literal>oci://"
"registry.suse.com/edge/charts</literal>"

