#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:582
msgid ""
"On the extension card click <literal>Install</literal> and confirm the "
"installation."
msgstr ""
"En la tarjeta de la extensión, haga clic en <literal>Install</literal> y "
"confirme el proceso."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:583
msgid ""
"Once the extension is installed Rancher UI prompts to reload the page as "
"described in the <literal><link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/rancher-"
"extensions#installing-extensions\">Installing Extensions Rancher "
"documentation page</link></literal>."
msgstr ""
"Una vez instalada la extensión, la interfaz de usuario de Rancher solicita "
"que se vuelva a cargar la página, tal y como se describe en la página "
"<literal><link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/"
"integrations-in-rancher/rancher-extensions#installing-"
"extensions\">Installing Extensions Rancher</link></literal> (Instalación de "
"extensiones de Rancher) de la documentación."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:584
msgid "Installing with Helm"
