msgstr ""
"El fragmento anterior nos indica que el componente <literal>Network</"
"literal> se ha configurado correctamente y que podemos continuar con el "
"aprovisionamiento de nuestros nodos periféricos."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><blockquote><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:769
msgid ""
"A log file (<literal>network-config.log</literal>) and the respective "
"NetworkManager connection files can be inspected in the resulting "
"<literal>_build</literal> directory under a timestamped directory for the "
"image run."
msgstr ""
"Es posible inspeccionar un archivo de registro (<literal>network-config.log</"
"literal>) y los respectivos archivos de conexión de NetworkManager en el "
"directorio <literal>_build</literal> resultante, dentro de un directorio con "
"marca de hora de la ejecución de la imagen."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:770
msgid "Provisioning the edge nodes"
msgstr "Aprovisionamiento de los nodos periféricos"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:771
msgid "Let’s copy the resulting RAW image:"
msgstr "Vamos a copiar la imagen RAW resultante:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:772
msgid ""
"You will notice that we copied the built image four times but only specified "
"the network configurations for three nodes.  This is because we also want to "
"showcase what will happen if we provision a node which does not match any of "
"the desired configurations."
msgstr ""
"Notará que hemos copiado la imagen creada cuatro veces, pero solo "
"especificamos las configuraciones de redes para tres nodos. Esto se debe a "
"que también queremos mostrar lo que sucederá si aprovisionamos un nodo que "
"no coincide con ninguna de las configuraciones deseadas."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><blockquote><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:773
msgid ""
"This guide will use virtualization for the node provisioning examples. "
"Ensure the necessary extensions are enabled in the BIOS (see <link "
"xl:href=\"https://documentation.suse.com/sles/15-SP6/html/SLES-all/cha-virt-"
"support.html#sec-kvm-requires-hardware\">here</link> for details)."
msgstr ""
"En esta guía se usará virtualización para los ejemplos de aprovisionamiento "
"de nodos. Asegúrese de que estén habilitadas las extensiones necesarias en "
"el BIOS (consulte <link xl:href=\"https://documentation.suse.com/sles/15-SP6/"
"html/SLES-all/cha-virt-support.html#sec-kvm-requires-hardware\">este "
"documento</link> para obtener más detalles)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:774
msgid ""
"We will be using <literal>virt-install</literal> to create virtual machines "
"using the copied raw disks.  Each virtual machine will be using 10 GB of RAM "
"and 6 vCPUs."
msgstr ""
"Utilizaremos <literal>virt-install</literal> para crear máquinas virtuales "
"utilizando los discos sin procesar copiados. Cada máquina virtual utilizará "
"10 GB de RAM y 6 CPU virtuales."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:775
msgid "Provisioning the first node"
msgstr "Aprovisionamiento del primer nodo"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:776 l10n/source/edge.xml:789 l10n/source/edge.xml:794
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:800
msgid "Let’s create the virtual machine:"
msgstr "Vamos a crear la máquina virtual:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><blockquote><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:777
msgid ""
"It is important that we create the network interfaces with the same MAC "
"addresses as the ones in the desired state we described above."
msgstr ""
"Es importante que creemos las interfaces de red con las mismas direcciones "
"MAC que las del estado deseado que hemos descrito anteriormente."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:778
msgid ""
"Once the operation is complete, we will see something similar to the "
"following:"
msgstr "Una vez completada la operación, veremos algo similar a lo siguiente:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:779
msgid ""
"We’re now able to log in with the <literal>root:eib</literal> credentials "
"pair.  We’re also able to SSH into the host if we prefer that over the "
"<literal>virsh console</literal> we’re presented with here."
msgstr ""
"Ahora podemos iniciar sesión con el par de credenciales <literal>root:eib</"
"literal>. Si lo preferimos, también podemos conectarnos por SSH al host, en "
"lugar de a la <literal>consola virsh</literal> que se presenta aquí."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:780
msgid "Once logged in, let’s confirm that all the settings are in place."
msgstr ""
"Cuando haya iniciado sesión, confirmaremos que todos los ajustes estén "
"correctos."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:781
msgid "Verify that the hostname is properly set:"
msgstr "Verifique que el nombre de host esté configurado correctamente:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:782 l10n/source/edge.xml:811 l10n/source/edge.xml:827
msgid "Verify that the routing is properly configured:"
msgstr "Verifique que la configuración de enrutamiento sea correcta:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:783 l10n/source/edge.xml:812 l10n/source/edge.xml:828
msgid "Verify that Internet connection is available:"
msgstr "Verifique que la conexión a Internet esté disponible:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:784
msgid ""
"Verify that exactly two Ethernet interfaces are configured and only one of "
"those is active:"
msgstr ""
"Verifique que haya exactamente dos interfaces Ethernet configuradas y que "
"solo una de ellas esté activa:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:785
msgid ""
"You’ll notice that the second interface is <literal>eth1</literal> instead "
"of the predefined <literal>eth3</literal> in our desired networking state.  "
"This is the case because the NetworkManager Configurator (<emphasis>nmc</"
"emphasis>) is able to detect that the OS has given a different name for the "
"NIC with MAC address <literal>34:8a:b1:4b:16:e2</literal> and it adjusts its "
"settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Notará que la segunda interfaz es <literal>eth1</literal> en lugar de la "
"predefinida en nuestro estado de red deseado, <literal>eth3</literal>. Esto "
"se debe a que NetworkManager Configurator (<emphasis>nmc</emphasis>) es "
"capaz de detectar que el sistema operativo ha asignado un nombre diferente a "
"la tarjeta de red con la dirección MAC <literal>34:8a:b1:4b:16:e2</literal> "
"y ajusta su configuración en consecuencia."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:786
msgid ""
"Verify this has indeed happened by inspecting the Combustion phase of the "
"provisioning:"
msgstr ""
"Verifique que, efectivamente, esto sea así inspeccionando la fase de "
"Combustion del aprovisionamiento:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:787
msgid ""
"We will now provision the rest of the nodes, but we will only show the "
"differences in the final configuration.  Feel free to apply any or all of "
"the above checks for all nodes you are about to provision."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, aprovisionaremos el resto de los nodos, pero solo mostraremos las "
"diferencias en la configuración final. No dude en aplicar cualquiera de las "
"comprobaciones anteriores, o todas ellas, a todos los nodos que vaya a "
"aprovisionar."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:788
msgid "Provisioning the second node"
msgstr "Aprovisionamiento del segundo nodo"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:790
msgid ""
"Once the virtual machine is up and running, we can confirm that this node is "
"using bonded interfaces:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando la máquina virtual esté activa y en funcionamiento, se puede "
"confirmar que este nodo está utilizando interfaces vinculadas:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:791
msgid "Confirm that the routing is using the bond:"
msgstr "Confirme que el enrutamiento utiliza la vinculación de interfaces:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:792 l10n/source/edge.xml:797
msgid "Ensure that the static connection files are properly utilized:"
msgstr ""
"Asegúrese de que los archivos de conexión estática se utilicen correctamente:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:793
msgid "Provisioning the third node"
msgstr "Aprovisionamiento del tercer nodo"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:795
msgid ""
"Once the virtual machine is up and running, we can confirm that this node is "
"using a network bridge:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando la máquina virtual está activa y en funcionamiento, se puede "
"confirmar que este nodo está utilizando un puente de red:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:796
msgid "Confirm that the routing is using the bridge:"
msgstr "Confirme que el enrutamiento utiliza el puente:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:798
msgid "Provisioning the fourth node"
msgstr "Aprovisionamiento del cuarto nodo"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:799
msgid ""
"Lastly, we will provision a node which will not match any of the predefined "
"configurations by a MAC address.  In these cases, we will default to DHCP to "
"configure the network interfaces."
msgstr ""
"Por último, se aprovisionará un nodo que no coincida con ninguna de las "
"configuraciones predefinidas por una dirección MAC. En estos casos, "
"utilizaremos DHCP de forma predeterminada para configurar las interfaces de "
"red."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:801
msgid ""
"Once the virtual machine is up and running, we can confirm that this node is "
"using a random IP address for its network interface:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando la máquina virtual esté activa y en funcionamiento, podemos confirmar "
"que este nodo utiliza una dirección IP aleatoria para su interfaz de red:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:802
msgid "Verify that nmc failed to apply static configurations for this node:"
msgstr ""
"Verifique que nmc no ha podido aplicar configuraciones estáticas para este "
"nodo:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:803
msgid "Verify that the Ethernet interface was configured via DHCP:"
msgstr "Verifique que la interfaz Ethernet se haya configurado mediante DHCP:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:804
msgid "Unified node configurations"
msgstr "Configuraciones unificadas de nodos"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:805
msgid ""
"There are occasions where relying on known MAC addresses is not an option. "
"In these cases we can opt for the so-called <emphasis>unified configuration</"
"emphasis> which allows us to specify settings in an <literal>_all.yaml</"
"literal> file which will then be applied across all provisioned nodes."
msgstr ""
"Hay ocasiones en las que no es posible basarse en direcciones MAC conocidas. "
"En esos casos, podemos optar por la denominada <emphasis>configuración "
"unificada</emphasis>, que permite especificar los ajustes en un archivo "
"<literal>_all.yaml</literal> que luego se aplicará a todos los nodos "
"aprovisionados."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:806 l10n/source/edge.xml:817
msgid ""
"We will build and provision an edge node using different configuration "
