"There are several ways to install SUSE Storage on your Kubernetes clusters.  "
"This guide will follow through the Helm installation, however feel free to "
"follow the <link xl:href=\"https://longhorn.io/docs/1.9.1/deploy/install/"
"\">official documentation</link> if another approach is desired."
msgstr ""
"Hay varias formas de instalar SUSE Storage en los clústeres de Kubernetes. "
"Esta guía explica la instalación con Helm, pero si desea usar otro método, "
"puede seguir la <link xl:href=\"https://longhorn.io/docs/1.9.1/deploy/"
