msgstr "Acceso al panel de control de la máquina virtual"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1061
msgid ""
"The \"Virtual machines\" list provides a <literal>Console</literal> drop-"
"down list that allows to connect to the machine using <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">VNC or Serial Console</emphasis>. This action is only "
"available to running machines."
msgstr ""
"La lista \"Virtual Machines\" (Máquinas virtuales) proporciona una lista "
"desplegable <literal>Console</literal> (Panel de control) que permite "
"conectarse a la máquina mediante <emphasis role=\"strong\">VNC o un panel de "
"control serie</emphasis>. Esta acción solo está disponible para máquinas en "
"ejecución."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1062
msgid ""
"In some cases, it takes a short while before the console is accessible on a "
"freshly started virtual machine."
msgstr ""
"En algunos casos, para poder acceder al panel de control en una máquina "
"virtual recién iniciada se debe esperar un poco."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1063
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"vnc-console-ui.png\" width=\"\"/> </"
"imageobject>"
