#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1245
msgid ""
"Here you can view every component that the Upgrade Controller will try to "
"schedule an upgrade for. Each condition follows the below template:"
msgstr ""
"Aquí puede ver todos los componentes para los que Upgrade Controller "
"intentará programar una actualización. Cada condición sigue el siguiente "
"formato:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1246
msgid ""
"<literal>lastTransitionTime</literal> - the last time that this component "
"condition has transitioned from one status to another."
msgstr ""
"<literal>lastTransitionTime</literal>: la hora a la que esta condición del "
"componente pasó de un estado a otro por última vez."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1247
msgid ""
"<literal>message</literal> - message that indicates the current upgrade "
"state of the specific component condition."
msgstr ""
"<literal>message</literal>: mensaje que indica el estado actual de "
"actualización de la condición específica del componente."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1248
msgid ""
"<literal>reason</literal> - the current upgrade state of the specific "
"component condition. Possible <literal>reasons</literal> include:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>reason</literal>: el estado actual de actualización de la condición "
"específica del componente. Los valores posibles para <literal>reasons</"
"literal> son:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1249
msgid ""
"<literal>Succeeded</literal> - upgrade of the specific component is "
"successful."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Succeeded</literal>: la actualización del componente específico se "
"ha realizado correctamente."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1250
msgid ""
"<literal>Failed</literal> - upgrade of the specific component has failed."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Failed</literal>: la actualización del componente específico ha "
"fallado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1251
msgid ""
"<literal>InProgress</literal> - upgrade of the specific component is "
"currently in progress."
msgstr ""
"<literal>InProgress</literal>: la actualización del componente específico "
"está en curso."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1252
msgid ""
"<literal>Pending</literal> - upgrade of the specific component is not yet "
"scheduled."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Pending</literal>: la actualización del componente específico aún "
"no se ha programado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1253
msgid ""
"<literal>Skipped</literal> - specific component is not found on the cluster, "
"so its upgrade will be skipped."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Skipped</literal>: el componente específico no se encuentra en el "
"clúster, por lo que se omitirá su actualización."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1254
msgid ""
"<literal>Error</literal> - specific component has encountered a transient "
"error."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Error</literal>: se ha producido un error transitorio en un "
"componente específico."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1255
msgid ""
"<literal>status</literal> - status of the current condition <literal>type</"
"literal>, one of <literal>True</literal>, <literal>False</literal>, "
"<literal>Unknown</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>status</literal>: el estado de <literal>type</literal> (tipo) de la "
"condición actual. Puede ser <literal>True</literal> (Verdadero), "
"<literal>False</literal> (Falso) o <literal>Unknown</literal> (Desconocido)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1256
msgid ""
"<literal>type</literal> - indicator for the currently upgraded component."
msgstr ""
"<literal>type</literal>: indicador del componente actualmente actualizado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1257
msgid ""
"The Upgrade Controller creates SUC Plans for component conditions of type "
"<literal>OSUpgraded</literal> and <literal>KubernetesUpgraded</literal>. To "
"further track the SUC Plans created for these components, refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller-monitor-plans\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Upgrade Controller crea planes de SUC para las condiciones de componentes de "
"tipo <literal>OSUpgraded</literal> y <literal>KubernetesUpgraded</literal>. "
"Para realizar un seguimiento más detallado de los planes de SUC creados para "
"estos componentes, consulte la <xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-"
"controller-monitor-plans\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1258
msgid ""
"All other component condition types can be further tracked by viewing the "
"resources created for them by the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/"
"helm-controller/\">helm-controller</link>. For more information, see <xref "
"linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-track-helm\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Es posible seguir realizando un seguimiento de todos los demás tipos de "
"condiciones de los componentes mediante la visualización de los recursos "
"creados para ellos por <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/helm-"
"controller/\">helm-controller</link>. Para obtener más información, consulte "
"la <xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-track-helm\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1259
msgid ""
"An Upgrade Plan scheduled by the Upgrade Controller can be marked as "
"<literal>successful</literal> once:"
