msgstr ""
"No hay condiciones de componentes con el estado <literal>Pending</literal> o "
"<literal>InProgress</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1261
msgid ""
"The <literal>lastSuccessfulReleaseVersion</literal> property points to the "
"<literal>releaseVersion</literal> that is specified in the Upgrade Plan’s "
"configuration. <emphasis>This property is added to the Upgrade Plan’s status "
"by the Upgrade Controller once the upgrade process is successful.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"La propiedad <literal>lastSuccessfulReleaseVersion</literal> apunta a la "
"versión de <literal>releaseVersion</literal> especificada en la "
"configuración de UpgradePlan. <emphasis>Upgrade Controller añade esta "
"propiedad al estado de UpgradePlan después de que el proceso de "
"actualización se ha completado correctamente.</emphasis>"

