msgstr "A continuación, encontrará un diagrama de la descripción anterior:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1854
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-day2-management-os-upgrade.png\" "
