msgstr "actualización de sistema operativo de gestión de día 2 con fleet"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1856 l10n/source/edge.xml:1976
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2364 l10n/source/edge.xml:2481
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Requisitos"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1857 l10n/source/edge.xml:2365
msgid "<emphasis>General:</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Generales:</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1858
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SCC registered machine</emphasis> - All management "
"cluster nodes should be registered to <literal><link xl:href=\"https://"
"scc.suse.com/\">https://scc.suse.com/</link></literal> which is needed so "
"that the respective <literal>systemd.service</literal> can successfully "
"connect to the desired RPM repository."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Equipo registrado en el Centro de servicios al "
"cliente de SUSE</emphasis>. Todos los nodos del clúster de gestión deben "
"estar registrados en <literal><link xl:href=\"https://scc.suse.com/"
"\">https://scc.suse.com/</link></literal>. Esto es necesario para que el "
"servicio <literal>systemd.service</literal> respectivo pueda conectarse "
"correctamente al repositorio de RPM deseado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1859 l10n/source/edge.xml:2367
msgid ""
"For Edge releases that require an OS version migration (e.g. <literal>6.0</"
"literal> → <literal>6.1</literal>), make sure that your SCC key supports the "
"migration to the new version."
msgstr ""
"Para las versiones de Edge que requieren una migración de la versión del "
"sistema operativo (por ejemplo, de la <literal>6.0</literal> a la "
"<literal>6.1</literal>), asegúrese de que su clave del Centro de servicios "
"al cliente de SUSE admita la migración a la nueva versión."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1860 l10n/source/edge.xml:2368
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Make sure that SUC Plan tolerations match node "
"tolerations</emphasis> - If your Kubernetes cluster nodes have custom "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">taints</emphasis>, make sure to add <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/scheduling-eviction/taint-and-"
"toleration/\">tolerations</link> for those taints in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis>. By default, <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis> have tolerations only for <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">control-plane</emphasis> nodes. Default tolerations include:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Asegúrese de que las tolerancias del plan de SUC "
"coincidan con las tolerancias de los nodos</emphasis>. Si los nodos de su "
"clúster de Kubernetes tienen <emphasis role=\"strong\">intolerancias "
"(taints)</emphasis> personalizadas, asegúrese de añadir <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/scheduling-eviction/taint-and-"
