#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2217 l10n/source/edge.xml:2713
msgid ""
"For an environment that supports GitOps (e.g. is non air-gapped, or is air-"
"gapped, but allows for local Git server support):"
msgstr ""
"En un entorno que admita GitOps (por ejemplo, que no esté aislado, o que "
"esté aislado pero permita la asistencia de un servidor Git local):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2218 l10n/source/edge.xml:2714
msgid ""
"Copy the <literal>fleets/day2/eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet to the "
"repository that you will use for GitOps."
msgstr ""
"Copie la flota <literal>fleets/day2/eib-charts-upgrader</literal> en el "
"repositorio que usará para GitOps."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2219 l10n/source/edge.xml:2715
msgid ""
"Make sure that the Fleet includes the changes that have been made by the "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script."
msgstr ""
"Asegúrese de que la flota incluye los cambios realizados por el guion "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2220 l10n/source/edge.xml:2716
msgid ""
"Configure a <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource that will be used to ship "
"all the resources of the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet."
msgstr ""
"Configure un recurso <literal>GitRepo</literal> que se usará para incluir "
"todos los recursos de la flota <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2221 l10n/source/edge.xml:2717
msgid ""
"For <literal>GitRepo</literal> configuration and deployment through the "
"Rancher UI, see <link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/"
"v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-"
"ui\">Accessing Fleet in the Rancher UI</link>."
msgstr ""
"Para la configuración y el despliegue de <literal>GitRepo</literal> mediante "
"la interfaz de usuario de Rancher, consulte <link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/"
"overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-ui\">Accessing Fleet in the Rancher "
"UI</link> (Acceso a Fleet en la interfaz de usuario de Rancher)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2222 l10n/source/edge.xml:2718
msgid ""
"For <literal>GitRepo</literal> manual configuration and deployment, see "
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/tut-deployment\">Creating a "
"Deployment</link>."
msgstr ""
"Para la configuración y el despliegue manuales de <literal>GitRepo</"
"literal>, consulte <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/tut-"
"deployment\">Creating a Deployment</link> (Creación de un despliegue)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2223 l10n/source/edge.xml:2719
msgid ""
"For an environment that does not support GitOps (e.g. is air-gapped and does "
"not allow local Git server usage):"
msgstr ""
"En un entorno que no admita GitOps (por ejemplo, un entorno aislado que no "
"permita el uso de un servidor Git local):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2224 l10n/source/edge.xml:2720
msgid ""
"Download the <literal>fleet-cli</literal> binary from the <literal>rancher/"
"fleet</literal> <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/fleet/releases/"
"tag/v0.13.1\">release</link> page (<literal>fleet-linux-amd64</literal> for "
"Linux). For Mac users, there is a Homebrew Formulae that can be used - <link "
"xl:href=\"https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/fleet-cli\">fleet-cli</link>."
msgstr ""
"Descargue el binario de <literal>fleet-cli</literal> de la página de <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/fleet/releases/tag/v0.13.1\">versión</"
"link> de <literal>rancher/fleet</literal> (<literal>fleet-linux-amd64</"
"literal> para Linux). Los usuarios de Mac pueden usar una versión propia: "
"<link xl:href=\"https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/fleet-cli\">fleet-cli</"
"link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2225 l10n/source/edge.xml:2721
msgid "Navigate to the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet:"
msgstr "Diríjase a la flota <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2226 l10n/source/edge.xml:2722
msgid ""
"Create a <literal>targets.yaml</literal> file that will instruct Fleet where "
"to deploy your resources:"
msgstr ""
"Cree un archivo <literal>targets.yaml</literal> que indicará a Fleet dónde "
"debe desplegar los recursos:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2229 l10n/source/edge.xml:2724
msgid ""
"Use the <literal>fleet-cli</literal> to convert the Fleet to a "
"<literal>Bundle</literal> resource:"
msgstr ""
"Utilice <literal>fleet-cli</literal> para convertir la flota en un recurso "
"<literal>Bundle</literal>:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2230 l10n/source/edge.xml:2725
msgid ""
"This will create a Bundle (<literal>bundle.yaml</literal>) that will hold "
"all the templated resource from the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> "
"Fleet."
msgstr ""
"Esto creará un Bundle (<literal>bundle.yaml</literal>) que contendrá todos "
"los recursos de plantilla de la flota <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2231 l10n/source/edge.xml:2726
msgid ""
"For more information regarding the <literal>fleet apply</literal> command, "
"see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/"
"fleet_apply\">fleet apply</link>."
msgstr ""
"Para obtener más información sobre el comando <literal>fleet apply</"
"literal>, consulte <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/"
"fleet_apply\">fleet apply</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2232 l10n/source/edge.xml:2727
msgid ""
"For more information regarding converting Fleets to Bundles, see <link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-chart-into-a-"
"bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle</link>."
msgstr ""
"Para obtener más información sobre cómo convertir flotas en Bundles, "
"consulte <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-"
"chart-into-a-bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle</link> (Conversión "
"de un chart de Helm en un Bundle)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2233 l10n/source/edge.xml:2728
msgid ""
"Deploy the <literal>Bundle</literal>. This can be done in one of two ways:"
msgstr "Despliegue el <literal>Bundle</literal>. Puede hacerlo de dos formas:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2234 l10n/source/edge.xml:2729
msgid ""
"Through Rancher’s UI - Navigate to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Continuous "
"Delivery → Advanced → Bundles → Create from YAML</emphasis> and either paste "
"the <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> contents, or click the <literal>Read from "
"File</literal> option and pass the file itself."
msgstr ""
"Mediante la interfaz de usuario de Rancher: seleccione <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Continuous Delivery → Advanced → Bundles → Create from YAML</"
"emphasis> (Entrega continua → Avanzado → Bundles → Crear desde YAML) y pegue "
"el contenido de <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> o haga clic en la opción "
"<literal>Read from File</literal> (Leer desde archivo) y pase el archivo."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2235 l10n/source/edge.xml:2730
msgid ""
"Manually - Deploy the <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> file manually inside of "
"your <literal>management cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Manualmente: despliegue el archivo <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> "
"manualmente dentro de su <literal>clúster de gestión</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2236
msgid ""
"Executing these steps will result in a successfully deployed "
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> resource. The resource will be picked up "
"by Fleet and its contents will be deployed onto the target clusters that the "
"user has specified in the previous steps. For an overview of the process, "
"refer to <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-overview\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Al ejecutar estos pasos, se desplegará correctamente el recurso "
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal>. Fleet recogerá el recurso y su contenido "
"se desplegará en los clústeres de destino que el usuario haya especificado "
"en los pasos anteriores. Para obtener una descripción general del proceso, "
"consulte la <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-overview\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2237
msgid ""
"For information on how to track the upgrade process, you can refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-"
"upgrade-example\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Para obtener información sobre cómo realizar un seguimiento del proceso de "
"actualización, consulte la <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-example\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2238 l10n/source/edge.xml:2733
msgid ""
"Once the chart upgrade has been successfully verified, remove the "
"<literal>Bundle/GitRepo</literal> resource."
msgstr ""
"Cuando haya verificado que el chart se ha actualizado correctamente, elimine "
"el recurso <literal>Bundle/GitRepo</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2239
msgid ""
"This will remove the no longer necessary upgrade resources from your "
"<literal>management</literal> cluster, ensuring that no future version "
"clashes might occur."
msgstr ""
"Esto eliminará los recursos de actualización que ya no son necesarios del "
"clúster de <literal>gestión</literal>, lo que garantizará que no se "
"produzcan conflictos entre versiones en el futuro."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2240 l10n/source/edge.xml:2735
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Ejemplo"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2241
msgid ""
"The example below demonstrates how to upgrade a Helm chart deployed via "
"<literal>EIB</literal> from one version to another on a <literal>management</"
"literal> cluster. Note that the versions used in this example are <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">not</emphasis> recommendations. For version recommendations "
"specific to an Edge release, refer to the release notes (<xref "
"linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"El siguiente ejemplo muestra cómo actualizar un chart de Helm desplegado "
