#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3567
msgid ""
"The following sections show how to prepare the different scenarios for the "
"directed network provisioning workflow using SUSE Telco Cloud.  For examples "
"of the different configurations options for deployment (incl. air-gapped "
"environments, DHCP and DHCP-less networks, private container registries, "
"etc.), see the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/atip/tree/"
"release-3.4/telco-examples/edge-clusters\">SUSE Telco Cloud repository</"
"link>."
