"associated Secret containing an <literal>nmstate</literal> formatted "
"<literal>networkData</literal> block. The following example file defines a "
"secret containing the required <literal>networkData</literal> that requests "
"a static <literal>IP</literal> and <literal>VLAN</literal> for the "
"downstream cluster host:"
