#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4131
msgid ""
"When onboarding remote hosts using Elemental, a race condition between "
"<literal>dbus.service</literal> and <literal>elemental-system-agent.service</"
"literal> might occur, resulting in <literal>rancher-system-agent.service</"
"literal> on remote host to fail starting with errors similar to the one "
