#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <literal>brokerProperties</literal> field is a key/value store that "
#~ "will be exposed as additional environment variables to any pod requesting "
#~ "a discovered device."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "El campo <literal>brokerProperties</literal> es un almacén de claves/"
